column2: An eldritch force makes it hard to swim.
Take these if you want to leave.
The Gods laugh at your misfortune.
Feel free to come back later.
That one was just a practice run.
It's not a loss if you learned something.

The portal to your right will take you to Boss Rush.
You'll face all main bosses consecutively, in general order of difficulty.
Your wands, perks, and items will be left here.
Any boss that you haven't killed yet on this run will have 20% more health.
Taking too much damage will force you to leave Boss Rush, but don't worry!
You get unlimited attempts, and you won't take any real damage or die.
Good luck, adventurer!
The portal to your left will take you back.
A teleporting bolt that casts another spell once it expires
Small teleport bolt with death trigger
A short-lived teleporting bolt that casts another spell once it expires
Halts your vertical momentum for two seconds
Exposes the location of most nearby items
Destroys three nearby spells to create a random new one
